items.title: Northern Arc Capital IPO closes today; GMP up 60%; should you subscribe?
items.description: Northern Arc Capital IPO, which opened for public subscription on Monday, September 16, 2024, closes today

items.title: NTPC Green Energy files draft papers to raise $1.2 billion through IPO
items.description: The company, a unit of power producer NTPC, will only issue new shares, and existing shareholders will not sell any stake, the draft papers showed
